source:
TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SEQ_00<tab>Qhoterl Pasol faces an unprecedented dilemma: a disastrous deluge of dead deer delicacies.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
<var 1A 02 /var>* Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var>

Qhoterl Pasol veut faire des réserves de nourriture.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SEQ_01<tab>Deliver the requested items to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SEQ_01<tab>Livrer ce qui vous a été demandé à Qhoterl Pasol

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Mine splendid rock salt in the K'mul Astropolis)) ((Deliver the splendid rock salt to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Gather splendid tree bark in the K'mul Astropolis)) ((Deliver the splendid tree bark to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Spearfish a splendid Night's bass in the depths of Lake Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Deliver the splendid Night's bass to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Extraire <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060302 /var> à l'Astropole des K'mul)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060302 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Récolter <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060302 /var> à l'Astropole des K'mul)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060302 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Harponner <var 33 ((Item)) 02E8060202 /var> dans le lac Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Livrer <var 33 ((Item)) 03E8060202 /var> à Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Our Viis friends have presented us with an enormous haul of venison as a sign of their appreciation for our work. The only problem is, there's so much of it, we'll need to smoke the meat before it goes rotten!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Gentilles Viis avoir offert viande de daine bleue à Qitari en gage d'amitié<var 1D /var>! Qhoterl Pasol vouloir fumer bons gros bouts de viande pour conserver longtemps longtemps<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Could I be awfully impertinent and ask you to bring me some rock salt? Sprinkling it on the meat beforehand draws out the rich, gamey flavors!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller à Astropole des K'mul et extraire trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273590302 /var> pour bien saler viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>Could I be awfully impertinent and ask you to bring me some tree bark? Naturally, only the most splendid will suffice.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller à Astropole des K'mul et récolter trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273730302 /var> pour bien aromatiser viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_003<tab>Could I be awfully impertinent and ask you to spear me a Night's bass? It may not be the most obvious choice, but apparently, smoking it together with the deer meat helps to preserve it.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_003<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller harponner <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF2738D0202 /var> dans lac Tusi Mek'ta pour accompagner viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_004<tab>If I could tear myself away from my duties here, I'd probably start by searching around the K'mul Astropolis. Something about the place simply screams “splendid,” wouldn't you agree?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_004<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller à Astropole des K'mul et extraire trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273590302 /var> pour bien saler viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_005<tab>If I could tear myself away from my duties here, I'd probably start by searching around the K'mul Astropolis. Something about the place simply screams “splendid,” wouldn't you agree?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_005<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller à Astropole des K'mul et récolter trois <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF273730302 /var> pour bien aromatiser viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_006<tab>If I could tear myself away from my duties here, and I had even the slightest inkling of how spearfishing works, I'd probably try my luck at Lake Tusi Mek'ta.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_006<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> aller harponner <var 33 ((Item)) 0DF2738D0202 /var> dans lac Tusi Mek'ta pour accompagner viande avant de fumer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SYSTEM_000_007<tab>In order to proceed with this quest, you must first complete the quest “A New Fishing Ex-spear-ience” and unlock spearfishing.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_SYSTEM_000_007<tab>Il est nécessaire de terminer la quête “La pêche au harpon, c'est bon” pour progresser dans celle-ci.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Have you brought that which I requested? Time is of the essence!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>(renifle) (renifle)... Toi sentir très bon<var 1D /var>! Petit doigt de Qhoterl Pasol dire que toi avoir rapporté nécessaire<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_011<tab>My word, this is splendid! Just the fragrance alone makes me want to gobble it all up, even without the venison...
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_011<tab>Miam miam<var 1D /var>! Tout être de hauuute qualité<var 1D /var>! Après avoir fumé viande selon technique ancestrale, Qitari se régaler pendant des semaines, oui oui<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_012<tab>Ah, of course, that would rather defeat the purpose of having you rush around before the meat spoils. And we wouldn't want the Viis' generous gift to go to waste, now, would we?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ116_03821_QHOTERLPASOL_000_012<tab>Quand explorateurs avoir ventre bien rempli, avoir tous sens en alerte<var 1D /var>! Trouuuver plein d'objets et même clic clic, hi hi<var 1D /var>!
